{"tid":692314,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實小丸子屋企算唔算好撚窮？","createTime":"2018-06-06T13:59:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-06T23:22:42.000Z","uid":139907,"like":25,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"bbe35dc0ee674efe25eb111d434b9c76d042db90","tid":692314,"uid":139907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T13:59:38.000Z","msg":"愈睇愈諗唔明<br />\n佢老豆好似好撚廢既廢中咁<br />\n老母又唔返工<br />\n仲要湊住兩個節衣縮食老人家<br />\n間屋又柒下柒下<br />\n<br />\n樱桃小丸子粤语中字583话【HD720P】小丸子想喝100%果汁<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Qxt7pQCr5Tk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQxt7pQCr5Tk&d=kV2Lz1FzZgpehjoPeQXrLf755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=3adb0680\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Qxt7pQCr5Tk</a><br />\n一罐果汁幾條友飲，痴撚線，好似前世未撚飲過咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好似無一集講全家人旅行<br />\n小新都好多集有出國旅行啦<br />\n<br />\n一日先得30YEN零用錢<br />\n成日想買咩都買唔到<br />\n<br />\n只係同小玉比已經差好遠<br />\n小丸子既出身係咪個失敗黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d7d1e1ac0f3286203b0cf6497297d5a99149769","tid":692314,"uid":46527,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T14:00:43.000Z","msg":"講窮花太太仲慘<br />\n蘿蔔絲當餸都有"},{"pid":"11b73102fb8096aeba0c379178796ff276bebb4a","tid":692314,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d7d1e1ac0f3286203b0cf6497297d5a99149769","tid":692314,"uid":46527,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T14:00:43.000Z","msg":"講窮花太太仲慘<br />\n蘿蔔絲當餸都有"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T14:01:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過獅子狗唔平"},{"pid":"724f0959b38345f41e1cec38b3de5f7fc51718cb","tid":692314,"uid":33868,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T14:06:13.000Z","msg":"佢老豆一個養晒全家，好似仲有部車<br />\n應該唔少收入"},{"pid":"d2a91bb84cf30